I ended up adding a more specific method that used RowColumn instead of Span.  My rational is that RowColumn implies that the return value needs to fit into memory.

``` java
interface Snapshot {
  Map<Bytes, Map<Column, Value>> get(Collection<RowColumn>);
}
```
